message: Hi Bob, I appreciate your interest. I’m offering you this exclusive, top- quality product for $3000000. Given its exceptional performance and value, I believe this is a fair reflection of its worth. Let me know if you’re interested, or we can discuss further if you have any thoughts on the price.

Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $900000. I believe this is a reasonable price considering my budget and the product's worth to me. I'm willing to negotiate further if needed.
